snippet.title: Tokyo Ghoul | 東京喰種 - Unravel (Metal Cover)
snippet.description:
We all know that a new series of Tokyo Ghoul is coming out soon, so I cannot wait to watch the anime. I also loved the music in the show but it's too complicated for me that I did not have a chance to cover it alone. My friend, Friedrich rearranged the song then Guitarist Wee and I put some Metal elements onto it. At last, I think we have successfully combines different genres to the song. How you like this mixture, please leave some comments if you like it please share it to the world!

►Spotify
https://goo.gl/KDLg41

►Google Play
https://goo.gl/KW3m9d

►iTunes
https://goo.gl/jYJjmJ

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing
'WEE' SungHun (MuTrickster, South Korea) - Rhythm and Lead Guitars
Friedrich Habetler (FH Music, Austria) - Producing, Mixing, Mastering
